This repository contains documentation, screenshots, architecture diagrams,
designs, and other materials describing the CareConnect Platform, which
comprises three mobile applications and a shared Supabase backend:

  - The Mother App (developed solely by Mozn Jamous)
  - The Admin Panel (developed solely by Mozn Jamous)
  - The Babysitter App (co-developed with @shaha123s)

The Mother App, the Admin Panel, the shared backend architecture, the
Figma design system, and the full IEEE 830 SRS document are the proprietary
and confidential property of Mozn Jamous.

The Babysitter App is jointly co-developed with @shaha123s. References to
that work in this repository describe Mozn Jamous's contributions only and
do not assign ownership of the joint work. For inquiries regarding the
Babysitter App source code, please contact @shaha123s directly.

